com.quest.glue.api.services
Interface CredentialEventProperties

public interface CredentialEventProperties

A collection of string property names that are commonly used when calling CredentialEvent.setProperty(java.lang.String, java.lang.String). None of these are required, nor are they the only acceptable property names. Agent developers are free to use whatever tags are required for their own use cases.

Field Summary
static java.lang.String TAGS
          The tags property defines a collection of arbitrary comma-separated strings.
 

Field Detail

TAGS

static final java.lang.String TAGS
The tags property defines a collection of arbitrary comma-separated strings. The strings don't have any particular meaning and are just keywords that can be used to determine the context of an event.

More details about tags and their uses can be found here.
